name: Walkover Web Solutions
overview:

It provides comprehensive web services ranging from Web hosting to development of complex enterprise web applications. The main aim of the company is to assist clients to evaluate, optimize and promote their web site in an effective manner that creates brand.

Currently it has developed renowned Web applications like MSG91, phone91, INeedName, Giddh, Save and Search,HostnSoft, and LifeTimeSEO.
